%C A001864 a(n) is the total number of nonrecurrent elements mapped into a recurrent element in all functions f:{1,2,...,n}->{1,2,...,n}.  a(n) = Sum_{k=1..n-1} A216971(n,k)*k. - _Geoffrey Critzer_, Jan 01 2013
